ista]]\n* Formats: LP, CS, CD\n| 3\n| \u2014\n| 3\n| 1\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| 8\n| \u2014\n| 1\n|\n* AUT: Gold<ref name=\"AUT CERT\"/>\n* [[Music Canada|CAN]]: Diamond<ref name=\"CAN CERT\">{{cite web|url=https://musiccanada.com/gold-platinum/?fwp_gp_search=ace%20of%20base |title=Canadian Certification |publisher=[[Music Canada]] |accessdate=15 October 2016}}</ref>\n* SWI: Platinum<ref name=\"SWI CERT\"/>\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|US]]: 9x Platinum<ref name=\"US CERT\">{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&se=ace+of+base#search_section |title=RIAA Certification |publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] |accessdate=16 October 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[The Bridge (Ace of Base album)|The Bridge]]''\n|\n* Released: 27 October 1995\n* Label: Edel-Mega\n* Formats: LP, CS, CD\n| 1\n| 46\n| 10\n| 9\n| 2\n| 29\n| 8\n| 4\n| 66\n| 29\n|\n* [[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|SWE]]: Gold<ref name=\"SWE CERT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.se/wp-content/uploads/guld-platina-1987-1998.pdf |title=Swedish Certifications |publisher=IFPI Sweden |accessdate=15 October 2016 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120521214300/http://www.ifpi.se/wp/wp-content/uploads/guld-platina-1987-1998.pdf |archivedate=21 May 2012 }}</ref>\n* CAN: 2x Platinum<ref name=\"CAN CERT\"/>\n* FIN: Platinum<ref name=\"FIN CERT\"/>\n* FRA: Platinum<ref name=\"FRA CERT\"/>\n* GER: Gold<ref name=\"GER CERT\"/>\n* SWI: Platinum<ref name=\"SWI CERT\"/>\n* US: Platinum<ref name=\"US CERT\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Flowers (Ace of Base album)|Flowers]]''\n|\n* Released: 15 June 1998\n* Label: Edel-Mega\n* Formats: CS, CD\n| 5\n| 217\n| 15\n| \u2014\n| 2\n| 16\n| 3\n| 1\n| 15\n| \u2014\n|\n* SWI: Gold<ref name=\"SWI CERT\"/>\n* UK: Silver<ref name=\"UK CERT\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''[[Cruel Summer (Ace of Base album)|Cruel Summer]]''\n|\n* Released: 25 August 1998\n* Label